gallery.beans

Class GalleryBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • gallery.beans.AbstractBean<Gallery>
      • gallery.beans.GalleryBean

  • @Path(value="/galleries")
public class GalleryBean
extends AbstractBean<Gallery>
    Gallery Enterprise Java Bean, maps to a Gallery Hibernate Entity. Also a REST service mapping to /YourPersonalPhotographOrganiser/resources/galleries.
